snippet: Texas A&M quarterback Johnny Manziel pleaded guilty Monday to a misdemeanor stemming from a 2012 bar fight near campus.
abstract: Texas A&M quarterback Johnny Manziel pleads guilty to a misdemeanor stemming from a 2012 bar fight near campus, and is ordered to pay a $2,000 fine and about $230 in court costs.
lead_paragraph: Texas A&M quarterback Johnny Manziel pleaded guilty Monday to a misdemeanor stemming from a 2012 bar fight near campus.

headline.main: Manziel Pleads Guilty to Bar Fight Charge
